{"tid":270252,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"坐小巴坐出面個位既人咩心態","createTime":"2017-06-04T08:15:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-04T08:42:03.000Z","uid":16073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aab65aa08bbf12ff5f7e36eb8f1f09f9243ed5cd","tid":270252,"uid":16073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T08:15:25.000Z","msg":"好想知 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係要空左入面個位坐出面個位<br />\n你坐低左 有人要坐 你又要郁 有人要出 你又要郁<br />\n你又煩 我又煩 <br />\n咁點解唔一開始坐入去 咩都唔使煩<br />\n<br />\n你話坐一兩個站我都理解 <br />\n但多數都唔係 坐到終站都係要坐出面<br />\n咩心態 想知好耐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9b2c4f0fe5c12e9d1bf0f66f1e9c6431c38bac2","tid":270252,"uid":53923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T08:22:00.000Z","msg":"好快落車<br />\n有啲小巴入面位好污漕<br />\n帶大件行李<br />\n坐入面要曬太陽<br />\n<br />\n以上係我諗到嘅原因<br />\n利申：無單人位就坐入面"},{"pid":"f4dfc2bb73671b232cf8d869573a2f016a494955","tid":270252,"uid":29382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T08:23:11.000Z","msg":"因為我好快樂"},{"pid":"8b194cbaebda93180a77990acbc0196ce213d9c8","tid":270252,"uid":86040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T08:33:17.000Z","msg":"唔想就人 所以要人地就你 自私心態"},{"pid":"a14e91f4545f1e59794d02f8cb8d18e5267a7ad5","tid":270252,"uid":16073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T08:37:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好快落車<br />\n有啲小巴入面位好污漕<br />\n帶大件行李<br />\n坐入面要曬太陽<br />\n<br />\n以上係我諗到嘅原因<br />\n利申：無單人位就坐入面</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試過好多次但都唔係以上原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都係 一定係坐入面"},{"pid":"2e20391e95a6f66f39b2cf2e8f6db5518681c8e8","tid":270252,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T08:38:55.000Z","msg":"想索下人個屁股 又同你講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffe4c8afb9c275bb18be0c64efd0e5b0d599e716","tid":270252,"uid":16073,"like":